      "acceptanceCriteria": "Iterative convergence tolerance verified to not contaminate hemolysis scalar transport solution; floating-point round-off analysis for rotating-frame hemolysis accumulation required.",
      "rationale": "Iterative convergence monitored via residuals but no formal analysis of solver error contribution to hemolysis QoI performed. Flagged as epistemic gap at MRL 5; achieved level set to 1 (no evidence)."
    },
