      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Documented simulation protocol with independent review of boundary condition setup, mesh generation, and post-processing scripts; at least one independent replication of a representative case.",
      "rationale": "No independent protocol review or replication performed. Single analyst responsible for all simulation setup and post-processing. Flagged as epistemic gap; achieved level 1."
    },
