      "acceptanceCriteria": "Full characterization of all uncertain model inputs (fluid properties, power-law coefficients, inlet velocity profiles) with probability distributions; Monte Carlo propagation to NIH with Sobol sensitivity indices.",
      "rationale": "Monte Carlo UQ performed on three inputs (inlet velocity, viscosity, rotor speed) but power-law exponents treated as fixed. Sobol indices not computed. Achieved level 3 reflects partial UQ without sensitivity decomposition."
    },
